{"type": "article", "id": 46032, "title": "一个丝袜品牌出了本杂志，反对社交媒体对裸体内容的审查不当", "description": "“裸体本身并不是有趣的，重要的是它背后的故事和信息。”", "date": "2017-10-12T05:30:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 44646, "name": "杂志排版"}, {"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 44647, "name": "Pan & The Dream"}, {"id": 44648, "name": "Paul Belford"}], "category": 17, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 125, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171018144142Q3ARF9fmG16y8PJl.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://www.panandthedream.com/products/pan-the-dream-issue-1-the-emperors-new-clothes\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pan &amp; The Dream</a> 是一个纽约时尚配饰品牌，主打产品是手工制作的高端丝袜。</p><p>这种丝袜以薄纱制成，自然垂坠不规则的褶皱是它的一大特色，微微蓬松的袜身，看似慵懒地堆在脚踝上，散发出独特的性感品味，有人将其形容为“飘着仙气的袜子”，像糖果一般能够满足少女心。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012130521tzwQndask7CTG2be.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012130521bRILHUErk7FfPevz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012130521GCUNhJmuvLlg1PzH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>最近，Pan &amp; The Dream 推出了一本品牌同名新杂志，第一期的主题是“皇帝的新衣”（The Emperor's New Clothes），限量 1000 份在全球发行，定价 69 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012130720kcngfv46lFS2CGWq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>他们找来了创意公司 <a href=\"http://paulbelford.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paul Belford </a>操刀杂志设计，其服务横跨广告、平面设计、包装设计等多个领域，比如为英菲尼迪 Q30、Q50 做的广告海报，以及为《经济学人》杂志做的广告装置等等。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.panandthedream.com/products/pan-the-dream-issue-1-the-emperors-new-clothes\" rel=\"nofollow\">在 Pan &amp; The Dream 团队看来</a>，“裸体本身并不是有趣的，重要的是它背后的故事和信息。”</p><p>这期杂志试图以优雅的形式展示裸体艺术。按照杂志的说法，这算是一个声明，是针对社交媒体上因为清教主义价值观对裸露内容审查不当的一种反抗和发声。它的目的是引起诸如 Instagram 和 Facebook 等社交媒体对类似审查行为的反思。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012130923xTOufhVH6anmR4iC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012130923Pz9qc6EpZJTt8CK3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012130924ZLvBH4MlygVnGcYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012130925ufrOwikdAxCKLW3R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012130926AumK07IDsHjEfbhk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012130926EpdyomWaXe9g580S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>包括 PetraBörner，Benoit Delhomme，Yvonne Gold，Tanya Linney 和 Isabel Reitemeyer 等艺术家都以摄影、插画等不同的方式描绘了裸体，试图回应艺术中的裸露议题以及裸露元素在媒体中遭遇的审查问题。而包括 Nadav Kander、Ken Schles、Nick Knight 和 Jock Sturges 等人，不管是备受尊重的艺术家，还是初初崭露头角的年轻创意人，都以访谈的形式谈论了上述议题。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012131040oG8UE46gwiCh9KMp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012131040CHtIerVPF2agXD0j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.522070\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012131040LBCNsol5IPYT8DrV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710121310404JZnOCLrXE8F5GvH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.245330\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>从采访文本到图片的表达，再结合杂志的设计与排版，Paul Belford 团队意在丰富大众对裸体艺术的认知，“它也许不是人们乍一眼看过去的直白裸露的观感那么肤浅、简单。”</p><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.creativereview.co.uk/paul-belford-designs-pan-dreams-new-magazine-naked-form/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Creative Review</a>、<a href=\"https://www.panandthedream.com/products/pan-the-dream-issue-1-the-emperors-new-clothes\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pan &amp; The Dream</a></p>"}